 Hololive的“家庭3D分发”是如何实现的？ Cover公司探秘追踪技术的幕后故事https://www.moguravr.com/hololive-3d-live-behind-the-scenes/ノンジャンル人生 Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:46:16 +0000 VTuberホロライブおうち3D配信 https://www.moguravr.com/?p=244989 <p>运营 VTuber 机构“Hololive Productions”的 Cover Co., Ltd. 在一份官方说明中发布了用于“家庭 3D 分发”的部分虚拟形象技术。 （摘自 Cover Co., Ltd. 官方说明）“Home 3D distribution”是 [...]</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/hololive-3d-live-behind-the-scenes/">Hololive的“家庭3D分发”是如何实现的？ Cover 对跟踪技术的幕后观察</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>运营 VTuber 机构“ <a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hololive Productions</a> ”的<a href="https://cover-corp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cover Co., Ltd.</a>在一份官方说明中发布了一些用于<strong>“家庭 3D 分发”</strong>的虚拟形象技术。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.y5nk0sm4qazc-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a><br /> （摘自<a href="https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cover Co., Ltd.官方说明</a>）</p><p> “家庭3D分发”是一种允许Hololive Production所属的VTuber在家中而不是在工作室进行3D分发的系统。不仅上半身直播，还实现了全身直播，以及Hololive VTuber之间的3D协作，成为粉丝们的热门话题。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.d202j8fm9x3c-768x430.webp 768w" width="800" height="448" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.pvaq6qtt8809-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.x7rr1on935el-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a></p><p>标题为“关于支持家庭 3D 分发的跟踪系统”的官方说明解释了跟踪机制。 VTuber的面部表情使用iPhone的ARKit。他透露，身体运动使用多种跟踪输入，包括移动动作捕捉“ <a href="https://www.sony.jp/mocopi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mocopi</a> ”、使用键盘的行走动作和选择性动画。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【首页3D凸等待】Pekomari被mocopi击败【Hololive/Hosho Marine/Pekora Usada】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ym83gIIc7vs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe><br /> （实际使用多个跟踪输入的流式传输）</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a></p><p>此外，还详细解释了Unity在计算人形模型姿态时的特殊情况。虽然内容严格来说是面向工程师的，但可以看出Hololive VTuber的3D分发并不是仅靠一套系统或设备实现的，而是多种技术融合的结果。</p><p>点击此处查看官方说明的详细信息。<br /> <a href="https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b</a></p><p> Cover Co., Ltd.一段时间以来一直在积极引进上述技术。此举看似是为了招募感兴趣领域的工程师，但通过公开公开不常在公开舞台上透露的专业技术部分，将为整个VTuber行业做出贡献，看来是有联系的到。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方说明</a></p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/hololive-3d-live-behind-the-scenes/">Hololive的“家庭3D分发”是如何实现的？ Cover 对跟踪技术的幕后观察</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
曾经有过这样的音乐现场形式吗？虚拟与现实的融合，透明LED的魅力“DOUBLE：”体验报告https://www.moguravr.com/double-report/けいろー Wed, 31 Jan 2024 09:55:06 +0000 VTuberActiv8 https://www.moguravr.com/?p=244919 <p> 2024 年 1 月 26 日。被誉为“现实与虚拟交叉的混合音乐节”的活动“DOUBLE:”在池袋harevutai举行。由 Activ8 赞助。它以创建 Kizuna AI 的公司而闻名 [...]</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/double-report/">使用透明 LED 实现虚拟与现实的融合：“DOUBLE：”体验报告</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> 2024 年 1 月 26 日。被誉为“现实与虚拟交叉的混合音乐节”的活动“ <strong>DOUBLE：</strong> ”在池袋harevutai举行。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>由<a href="https://activ8.co.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Activ8</a>赞助。不仅以制作Kizuna AI而闻名，近年来还制作了《ONE PIECE FILM RED》中出现的歌的3DCG模型，支援了《PROJECT IM@S vα-liv》的制作，主持VRChat活动，参与虚拟直播节目“CAPSULE Live in VRChat “Metropulse””的现场制作。</p><p>本次活动由Activ8主办。其最大的特点是<strong>虚拟与现实相结合的混合制作</strong>。预告中强调了“最先进的透明LED等数字技术”，表明这是一次新的尝试，不同于一般的Vtuber音乐现场。</p><p>事实上，艺术家阵容也别具一格。作为在二维和三维轴上工作的歌手，在音乐以外的领域受到关注的创作者。作为DJ的音乐制作人，活跃在以舞曲为主题的角色项目的第一线。这也感觉像是在不同背景下铸造了一位雄心勃勃的广义“表达”艺术家。</p><p>四位具有不同头衔和流派的艺术家将在 ACTIV8 赞助的活动中进行表演，这些活动一直在进行一些虚拟现场表演。那么你一定会看到一些新的、有趣的表达方式。在这篇文章中，我将向您讲述充满期待感的“DOUBLE:”模式。</p><h2>最先进的透明LED显示屏，投影效果清晰生动</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="DOUBLE: Vol.1 预告片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zvgWiVo5vGA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《DOUBLE:》是一首歌曲和表演，持续了大约两个半小时，现场剧场里挤满了观众。</p><p>整个现场的感想总结为一句话，“<strong>我感受到了‘虚拟’表达方式的可扩展性，以及Vtuber的音乐作为真实‘体验’的可能性</strong>。”当然，“我享受最好的音乐现场”是一个大前提。</p><p>其中最令人印象深刻的是同样提前推出的“最先进<strong>的透明LED</strong> ”。毫不夸张地说，这个透明 LED 是这场现场演出的核心。</p><p>首先，看下图。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>你明白吗？虚拟效果（Uzukaki）、真实表演者（DAOKO）、背景视频（浅蓝色视图），三者各有重叠。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>此外，在上图中，虚拟的长濑由香出现在真实的长濑由花面前。这是什么意思？</p><p>首先，在一般的现实世界Live House举行的“Vtuber的音乐Live”，让Vtuber可以在舞台上安装的大型显示器上进行表演。虽然也有虹山寺、Holo Live等大型现场表演中可以看到的AR制作，以及山葵音乐学校的真人大小虚拟形象现场系统等特殊的变化，但“显示投影”的风格是小型演出的主流。到中型活动。你可以这么说。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp 960w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-768x432.webp 768w" width="960" height="540" /></a><br /> （一般中型VTuber直播。如果有真人表演者，往往会出现在屏幕前面）</p><p>在这次的《DOUBLE:》中，Vtuber也以类似的风格进行投射，但与传统的有所不同。<strong>舞台背景安装了整个LED的高清显示屏后，靠近观众的舞台上又设置了一块大型透明LED显示屏，并且有一个VTuber/角色正在投影</strong>。</p><p>换句话说，就是下图这样的。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp 960w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-768x432.webp 768w" width="960" height="540" /></a><br /> （“DOUBLE：”的情况下：Vtuber出现在蓝色的透明LED中）</p><p>而且这种透明LED的透明度非常出色。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p><strong>一旦知道“有”，看起来很正常，但在演出之前，当赞助商视频流动时，不可能识别出那里的显示是“透明”的。</strong>现场表演开始了，顶级击球手凑小金学院，顶级击球手（黑铁小玉＆白金）出现在舞台上，当VJ开始在后面流动时，他终于“正在使用两个显示器。我明白了那。如果你在观众面前，你可能会立即注意到，但至少根本没有被捕捉到。</p><p>当我认识到透明 LED 的存在时，我对投影图像的美丽感到惊讶。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>在投影角色的实时情况下，根据显示器的性能，显色可能会感觉不舒服，可能会出现闪烁和残像。然而，舞台上出现的两位凑白金女子学院，不仅站姿清晰，而且没有丝毫的不适和模糊。<strong>飘逸的头发和衣摆的晃动都被清晰地描绘出来，就连激烈的舞蹈表演的锐利也被牢牢捕捉到。</strong></p><p>顺便说一句，除某些人以外，该直播被允许拍照和录制，但是如果您写道：“即使使用智能手机相机，也可以清楚地捕捉到透明LED上的外观和动作。”传播一点？实际性能发布在“ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hashtag_click" target="_blank" rel="noopener">#double_xr</a> ”中，因此，如果您有兴趣，请查看。</p><h2>透明LED被扩展的“实时”表达，以及真实X虚拟混合体验的深度</h2><p>顺便说一句，如前所述，两个显示器之间的真实表演者有一个阶段。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-682x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 682px) 100vw, 682px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-682x1024.webp 682w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-200x300.webp 200w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-768x1153.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-1023x1536.webp 1023w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-jpg.webp 1066w" width="682" height="1024" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>换句话说，<strong>显示的数量为两个，但是该层具有三个层状结构</strong>。真正的艺术家可以通过在两个显示器之间站立，不仅是大型展示，而且可以在观众身上安装的透明LED来表演。换句话说，<strong>您可以将虚拟生产带到“真实”方面</strong>。透明LED的存在不仅对Vtuber，而且对真正的艺术家都是有益的。</p><p> - 我想在现场的上半部分，但是过了一会儿，我意识到还有另一层。在演出期间，通过透明的唱歌唱歌的大科<a href="https://twitter.com/Daok0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">（Daoko）</a>在展示之前就出来了。从客观的角度来看，只有“唱歌艺术家搬到舞台的前面”，但是那时，我觉得自己好像已经搬到了太空中，“我可以来到这边！</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd