bp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.yvq8a2m28n9y-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>如果您开发了两个迷幻的VJ，它们刚刚称为颜色暴力，并与与身体核心产生共鸣的沉重低音一起，您将能够放开自己的想法和旅行。视觉和听力都托付给舞台上的艺术家，这是一次现场经历，就好像它只是将整个身体沉浸在音乐中一样。特别是，在表演tofubeats时，大脑对使用AI的VJ生产有很好的感觉，因此我希望您在其他俱乐部活动中将其纳入其中。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">我正在使用ai <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#double_xr</a> <a href="https://t.co/SnTty0KjIo">pic.twitter.com/sntty0kjio</a>实时生成tofbeats</p><p> -Toshini（@toshikuni_mayor） <a href="https://twitter.com/Toshikuni_Mayor/status/1750857992877355252?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年1月26日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>回顾上述作品和表达式的整个生活，这是一种听话的印象： <strong>“我认为表达式的宽度并不是通过增加显示器的数量而扩大的。”</strong></p><p>当然，这不是一个简单的故事，例如“仅”仅增加了显示屏。绝对使用高性能和高质量的LED显示器，并且在仔细调整后，应该实现深层生产的系统。此外，有必要考虑使观众感到更加三维的VJ，并且声音不会让您感到不舒服。您可以想象一下。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja"> 2024/1/26“ double：”<br />在Ikebukuro Harevutai</p><p> Huez负责指导，照明和VJ！<br />非常感谢！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#double</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#double_xr</a> <a href="https://t.co/btQBIUGsk5">pic.twitter.com/btqbiugsk5</a></p><p> -Huez（@huez_official） <a href="https://twitter.com/huez_official/status/1750872758697996468?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年1月26日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>然而，从听众的角度来看，我不禁要考虑这种尝试的“未来”。<strong>单独使用这种现场融合了各种各样的表达方法，但是如果您使用透明的LED，则应该可以做更多的事情</strong>。不仅在展示上投影，而且还展示了新的Vtuber音乐，与真正的艺术家合作，并在非生活中使用，例如戏剧和时装秀。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.st67tl6tij8g-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/