aku5_8_9_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">杠葉コハク</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/shikimi_hiiragi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">柊しきみ</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/usha_10181118" target="_blank" rel="noopener">雨紗</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/chiyuki_ankw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">姉川ちゆき</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/dadada_datarou" target="_blank" rel="noopener">駄ゞ田メダ</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/nyakoko_nyan" target="_blank" rel="noopener">天流にゃこ</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/miicha2528" target="_blank" rel="noopener">米夏</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/motikincha" target="_blank" rel="noopener">もちきんチャス</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/neko_tar1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">猫田リルカ</a><br /><a href="https://twitter.com/kiiiiichi_ss" target="_blank" rel="noopener">楽々きいち</a></p></blockquote><p>参考：X（旧Twitter）、<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000001.000126128.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">プレスリリース</a></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-usabit-dissolution/">VTuber事務所「usabit.」が解散 所属VTuberが給与未払いなど被害を訴え 事務所社長は失踪中との報告も</a>appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a> .</p> ;
